OL,5, A "dumbing down" of science at GCSE    
OL,6, level could see Wales "miss out on some
OL,7, brilliant scientists in the future", an
OL,8, academic has warned.                   
OL,10,FFrom 2025, physics, chemistry and      
OL,11,Fbiology will no longer be offered as   
OL,12,Fseparate subjects.                     
OL,14,FInstead, pupils will study for one     
OL,15,Fintegrated science award which combines
OL,16,Fthe three subjects and will be worth   
OL,17,Ftwo GCSEs.                             
OL,19,FQualifications Wales said integrating  
OL,20,Fsubjects allowed pupils a mix of GCSEs.
